{"tid":1245691,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開]班黑警原來唔係唔帶肩章 係特登帶反","createTime":"2019-06-20T12:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T13:43:44.000Z","uid":20294,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4878ae8424743e538dd030afc3b5c30434217b32","tid":1245691,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:03:58.000Z","msg":"原Link: 第一頁死link 再開<br />\n<br />\n班黑警原來唔係唔帶肩章 係特登帶反<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1245235\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1245235</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今次你仲唔含家產?</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/10/Wholefamdiethistime.png/revision/latest?cb=20140313152112\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F10%2FWholefamdiethistime.png%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20140313152112&h=af031c36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方俗稱速龍小隊的特別戰術小隊，難以識別身份問題引起關注。本台翻查上星期三金鐘衝突現場照片，發現在同一個速龍小隊，有隊員在胸前背心位置配戴肩章，有隊員無配戴肩章，亦有隊員懷疑將肩章前後倒轉配戴，遮蓋官階及警員編號。<br />\n<br />\n保安局長李家超昨日在立法會回應質詢時，引述警方資料，指速龍小隊工作服是依據行動和戰術需要而設計，無位置可以展示警員編號。本台已向警方查詢，暫時未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GJfhwUz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGJfhwUz.jpg&h=caa0b771&s={SIZE}\" /> <span style=\"font-size: medium;\">褐圈:有配戴肩章 藍圈:無配戴肩章 黃圈:前後倒轉配戴肩章</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TCnvRUL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTCnvRUL.jpg&h=47bcaf73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">黃圈:前後倒轉配戴肩章</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呢個要推</span></span><br />\n<br />\n疑似有人爆料<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#330<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>13182 陳漣蛟 屌你老母 戴反都認得你呀死矮撚 得果米六仲走去當差</blockquote>"},{"pid":"196da98e1671344f8a6d5c95d212ed55ae8b9336","tid":1245691,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:05:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"938378874e3f8768e290bb26c8eaff2a37e0f9d3","tid":1245691,"uid":20294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:05:54.000Z","msg":"推到個個 都知黑狗真垃圾"},{"pid":"7f2f495bb06fe0c63e47ecfa52aae5e4482fa530","tid":1245691,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:07:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38b72f4ef94879b1091f880d46184b37e05588a4","tid":1245691,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:09:26.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"3ddea2ac020135c049dd30b505e33963f0be46e3","tid":1245691,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:10:47.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"481c1f70738a690a1b2983537607a18d9c8a50f2","tid":1245691,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:13:43.000Z","msg":"推比人知"},{"pid":"69de092bb607a3bec94d31cc3112815f986c3022","tid":1245691,"uid":86610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:14:28.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"2d85a7db51cd6ab2489762993ccc60b1b894bb75","tid":1245691,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:16:00.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"444ff15afca50ea03fe19c4aec93d4169542b571","tid":1245691,"uid":20294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:16:42.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"69f5c4444574faa33fbd0487dc28a4a147d0d355","tid":1245691,"uid":261430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:17:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ab6ff78a45562a1c3165a0ab28fba032c6474e3","tid":1245691,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T12:18:08.000Z","msg":"黑警垃撚圾"},{"pid":"b00ed57734a0e406bc1b